commit.message: Merge branch 'readme'

Improve readme markup

* Syntax highlight for shell blocks
* Italics for file names
Remove deprecated Github Downloads installation method
Add Vim's license as another option

Fix cpoptions handling in syntax file

During a discussion on vim-dev several runtime files have been identified whose
handling of 'cpoptions' should be improved. You can re-read the whole
discussion at:
http://thread.gmane.org/gmane.editors.vim.devel/32151

The corresponding vim help is available at:
:help 'cpoptions'

This patch fixes one of those issues identified in a runtimefile.
